WEBVTT

1
00:00:09.100 --> 00:00:10.500
一名身着华丽刺绣长袍的女子低头站立，身后是手持长矛的侍卫。
A woman in an ornate, embroidered robe stands with her head bowed, guards holding spears stand behind her.

2
00:00:17.300 --> 00:00:19.500
夜色中的庭院里，一名男子在黑暗中挖土。
In the dark night garden, a man digs into the ground.

3
00:00:20.500 --> 00:00:23.500
他从窗户爬入屋中。
He climbs through a window into the house.

4
00:00:29.000 --> 00:00:35.000
夜幕下的古典花园中，小桥流水，亭台楼阁若隐若现。
A classical garden at night, with a small bridge over a stream and pavilions faintly visible.

5
00:00:38.000 --> 00:00:41.000
一名头戴鲜花、身穿红黄相间华服的女子走出房屋，缓步走向庭院。
A woman with flowers in her hair, wearing a red and yellow ornate dress, steps out of the house and walks slowly into the garden.

6
00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:50.000
男子躲在树丛后，窥视着女子。
The man hides behind bushes, peeking at the woman.

7
00:00:50.500 --> 00:00:52.000
女子面露忧色。
The woman shows a worried expression.

8
00:00:52.500 --> 00:00:55.000
男子从屋檐下探出头来。
The man peeks out from under the eaves of the roof.

9
01:00:00.000 --> 01:03:000
身着浅色长袍的姑爷从另一侧的门走出。
The young master, in light-colored robes, exits from a door on the other side.

10
01:04:000 --> 01:06:000
小姐看到了姑爷。
The Miss sees the young master.

11
01:28:000 --> 01:31:000
姑爷跪在地上，用手刨着泥土，小姐在一旁静静地看着他。
The young master kneels on the ground, digging at the soil with his hands, as the Miss watches him silently.

12
01:31:500 --> 01:32:500
姑爷用白布遮住了脸庞，似乎在哭泣。
The young master covers his face with a white cloth, seemingly weeping.

13
01:32:800 --> 01:34:000
小姐表情悲伤而担忧。
The Miss's expression is sad and worried.

14
01:47:000 --> 01:49:000
小姐和姑爷一同走向房屋。
The Miss and the young master walk together towards the house.

15
01:50:000 --> 01:52:000
姑爷在房屋入口处的石板下再次挖掘。
The young master digs again under a stone slab at the house entrance.

16
01:55:000 --> 01:56:000
姑爷抬起头，脸上露出绝望的神情。
The young master lifts his head, his face showing a desperate expression.

17
01:57:000 --> 01:58:000
小姐惊恐地看着姑爷。
The Miss looks at the young master in horror.

18
01:59:000 --> 02:01:000
姑爷猛地抓住小姐的手臂，小姐挣扎。
The young master abruptly grabs the Miss's arm, and she struggles.

19
02:01:000 --> 02:05:000
姑爷强行拉拽小姐。
The young master forcibly pulls the Miss.

20
02:06:500 --> 02:09:000
姑爷将小姐拖过小桥。
The young master drags the Miss across the small bridge.

21
02:12:000 --> 02:15:000
姑爷用铲子重击小姐头部，将其用白布包裹后拖走。
The young master strikes the Miss's head with a shovel, then wraps her in a white cloth and drags her away.

22
02:15:500 --> 02:16:500
姑爷迅速逃离。
The young master quickly flees.

23
02:16:500 --> 02:27:000
回到最初的场景，男子脸上挂着一抹狡黠的笑容。
Returning to the initial scene, the man wears a cunning smile.